  "detailed_description": "An abandoned Automata 'Yukiwari' awakens at the end of the sewers, in a graveyard of discarded Automata. Having lost her memory, she still embarks on a journey to reclaim the light her heart longs for - the 'Last Order.' <br><br>'Last Order' is a 2D action game with pixel art graphics and high difficulty. <br>Utilize a variety of wire actions to recover the Last Order in a devastated world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Offensive wire action</h2>In Last Order, wire actions are not just about movement.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Swing Wire</strong></li></ul>Swing wire is an action for movement and attack with wires strung across the ceiling.<br>Wires can cut off the enemies by passing, so it will be the primary means of attack.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/7a3fa4569805c94552523e35d41677d7.poster.avif?t=1723736246\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/7a3fa4569805c94552523e35d41677d7.webm?t=1723736246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/7a3fa4569805c94552523e35d41677d7.mp4?t=1723736246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dive Wire</strong></li></ul>Dive Wire is an action to move at high speed to scaffolds and to enemies by elastic wire.<br>You can break away from danger or Dive into the enemy freely.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/9403bc5b4cbc584331fb1ba680d28497.poster.avif?t=1723736246\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/9403bc5b4cbc584331fb1ba680d28497.webm?t=1723736246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/9403bc5b4cbc584331fb1ba680d28497.mp4?t=1723736246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Shackle Wire</strong></li></ul>Shackle Wire is an action to entangle and throw enemies or shells.<br>It can be used not only to shoot down enemies in the distance., but also as a defense to catch shells.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/0f82789afbeefe39498955cf85ebe425.poster.avif?t=1723736246\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/0f82789afbeefe39498955cf85ebe425.webm?t=1723736246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/0f82789afbeefe39498955cf85ebe425.mp4?t=1723736246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Growth to match your style</h2>Grow yourself according to your play style.<br>Power if you prefer short term battles, or resilience if you are prepared for long term battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/70227f4690dff791b5debd2fa807b8fd.avif?t=1723736246\" width=620 height=124 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize ability to fit situation</h2>Equip the order chips you obtained to gain new abilities.<br>Use the order chip according to the situation and your style.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/de7318e0f6ab4d4e6cc8da7d6fcad03c.avif?t=1723736246\" width=614 height=124 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exploration</h2>Items are hidden in the stages where automatas are abounded.<br>Exploration will help you find a key to your journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/45c6c5c45f2430ff49ba398f6479d027.avif?t=1723736246\" width=640 height=250 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tense boss battle</h2>Bosses with a wide variety of actions are powerful, but they are not overpowered difficulty.<br>Spot the pattern, bring down them with your skill and strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/d240014381076806999fb554768038cd.avif?t=1723736246\" width=620 height=230 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "An abandoned Automata 'Yukiwari' awakens at the end of the sewers, in a graveyard of discarded Automata. Having lost her memory, she still embarks on a journey to reclaim the light her heart longs for - the 'Last Order.' <br><br>'Last Order' is a 2D action game with pixel art graphics and high difficulty. <br>Utilize a variety of wire actions to recover the Last Order in a devastated world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Offensive wire action</h2>In Last Order, wire actions are not just about movement.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Swing Wire</strong></li></ul>Swing wire is an action for movement and attack with wires strung across the ceiling.<br>Wires can cut off the enemies by passing, so it will be the primary means of attack.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/7a3fa4569805c94552523e35d41677d7.poster.avif?t=1723736246\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/7a3fa4569805c94552523e35d41677d7.webm?t=1723736246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/7a3fa4569805c94552523e35d41677d7.mp4?t=1723736246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dive Wire</strong></li></ul>Dive Wire is an action to move at high speed to scaffolds and to enemies by elastic wire.<br>You can break away from danger or Dive into the enemy freely.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/9403bc5b4cbc584331fb1ba680d28497.poster.avif?t=1723736246\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/9403bc5b4cbc584331fb1ba680d2849