he stages where automatas are abounded.<br>Exploration will help you find a key to your journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/45c6c5c45f2430ff49ba398f6479d027.avif?t=1723736246\" width=640 height=250 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tense boss battle</h2>Bosses with a wide variety of actions are powerful, but they are not overpowered difficulty.<br>Spot the pattern, bring down them with your skill and strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132530/extras/d240014381076806999fb554768038cd.avif?t=1723736246\" width=620 height=230 /></span>",
